      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KEAYANG PASSION (4) is a three-year-old daughter of Stay Hungry on debut for the Lee yard. Has strong trial form coming into this, looking good in winning her hitout at Terang. Finds a nice race so anticipating a bright start to her career. KEAYANG ALABAMA (6) led and stuck on for second on debut at Kilmore before starting favourite when midfield at Hamilton on Monday. Draws wider but he is better than what he showed last time so is worth another chance. BUBBLE OVER (1) raced parked and finished 6 metres back in fifth on debut at Ballarat. Strips fitter and is well served by the ace draw so can improve. FANTASY FLIGHT (2) came from the back row when midfield on debut. A good draw can spark improvement.",
